Mr. Niraj Shah is a Technocrat & an avid businessman, most known for his work in the field of Industrial Automation & Humanized Robotics. He has more than 16 years of experience in the field of automation. He had started his automation journey with manufacturing of process instruments (more than 370 products) and portable control panels along with embedded software development. To provide a full spectrum of automation solutions he added sensors, security products, software and computers to his product line. He was also providing automation & hardware maintenance services at 7500+ locations in 6 states for companies like Reliance, SBI, BOB, SIDBI etc for more than 3 years. He is a mentor and motivator to various technical and management institutes. He has been providing technical consulting to many MNCs across IT, QA and IoT domains for more than 7 years. He has been doing research in the field of Humanized Robotics since 1998 (more than 17 years) and applied for various humanized robotics parts patents. Apart from above, he has been actively involved in the research work for electronics waste, non invasive glucometer, RFID based animal tracking and many more.  			
